			Beq.S		@2						; if not, skip this		** <C105/28aug86/MBK **

			Move.L		D3,A0					; return it in A0		** <C381/5nov86/MBK **
			Lea			inHandle+6(A6),A2		; pt to next param		** <C105/28aug86/MBK **
